- The next time I see, you better make sure the article is handled.

31:48.125 --> 31:54.750
and the person who wrote it
or you'll be the next person to be handled.

31:56.125 --> 31:58.125
- Yes Doctor

32:09.750 --> 32:11.750
♪♪

32:42.875 --> 32:44.875
[door opens]

32:58.625 --> 33:00.625
[grunting]

33:03.666 --> 33:05.666
[sobbing]

33:08.791 --> 33:10.791
[screaming]
[dustbin thudding]

33:14.500 --> 33:17.625
[breathes heavily]
[gunshots]

33:40.875 --> 33:42.875
[sobbing]

34:46.625 --> 34:48.375
- Hello Nora, how are you?

34:48.500 --> 34:54.375
- I'm not fine, I almost got killed yesterday.
There was a guy who was going through my stuff in my apartment and

34:54.500 --> 34:58.791
he tried to attack me Nkosi.
I was so scared, I-- I didn't know what to do.

35:02.750 --> 35:06.375
♪♪
- Walk with me Nora, I think you were followed.

35:23.541 --> 35:25.541
- Run.

36:03.291 --> 36:08.541
[screaming]
- Please get off!

36:09.166 --> 36:11.166
Nkosi!

36:17.375 --> 36:19.375
[engine revving]
[tyres screeching]

36:40.750 --> 36:42.750
- Bruh. How's it.
- Sho

36:44.416 --> 36:50.125
- The car is registered to Bongani Mlambo.
He stays right in CBD center. His address is right inside.

36:51.000 --> 36:53.000
- Thank you brother.
- Sho.

36:57.250 --> 36:59.250
♪♪

37:20.250 --> 37:22.250
♪♪

37:55.375 --> 37:57.375
[whistling]
[rhythmically clapping]

38:19.625 --> 38:21.625
[chanting]

38:35.041 --> 38:38.750
[gun cocks]
- Hey stay calm, where's the lady that you kidnapped?

38:39.250 --> 38:44.375
- What lady?
- I'll shoot you and I'll shoot everyone here if you do anything stupid, move!

38:44.750 --> 38:46.750
- Okay.

39:04.166 --> 39:06.166
- Stop, don't move stop.
[gunshots]

39:11.625 --> 39:13.625
I said stop, don't move.

39:17.375 --> 39:19.375
Stop. [gunshots]

39:19.500 --> 39:21.500
- Okay, okay.

39:25.375 --> 39:27.375
[gunshots]

39:28.291 --> 39:30.375
- Do you really think you're going to leave here alive.

39:30.625 --> 39:35.166
- I just want you to tell me where you are keeping the lady
and you are going to take me there.

39:41.250 --> 39:43.250
[gunshots]

39:47.666 --> 39:52.375
[grunting]
Listen to me, if I mention the right location all right,

39:52.500 --> 39:54.500
just blink your eye all right.

39:57.625 --> 40:03.875
Soweto?
Alex? Where in Alex man? Where in Alex man?

40:28.750 --> 40:30.750
[engine starts]

40:45.666 --> 40:47.666
[car indicators on]

40:50.291 --> 40:52.291
[phone rings]

40:58.000 --> 41:00.000
- Nkosi, how's it bruh?

41:00.125 --> 41:05.250
- I'm okay, I just sent you the number.
Can you please find the location of that number.

41:05.416 --> 41:08.625
- Oh, okay, give me a few seconds.
- Okay thank you.

41:13.250 --> 41:15.250
[engine revving]

41:29.000 --> 41:31.000
[car indicators on]
[phone chimes]

41:36.666 --> 41:38.666
♪♪

42:24.625 --> 42:26.625
[gunshot]

42:34.875 --> 42:36.875
[dice shaking]

42:52.500 --> 42:54.500
- Malahla

42:55.291 --> 42:57.291
- Malahla

43:02.041 --> 43:05.500
[indistinct conversation]

43:16.166 --> 43:18.625
- Take the gag off.

43:23.791 --> 43:25.791
[Nora spitting]

43:28.916 --> 43:30.000
[sniffles]

43:30.250 --> 43:34.000
- Tell me... who are you working for?

43:56.500 --> 43:59.250
[gunshots]

44:21.875 --> 44:23.875
- Who else knows about this?

44:34.375 --> 44:36.375
[gunshots continue]

44:56.750 --> 45:03.625
- Do you think this makes you a strong man?
You are nothing but a weak man who's being controlled by an evil man huh.

45:03.791 --> 45:06.791
How do you even sleep at night, pathetic human being.

45:08.125 --> 45:10.125
[screaming]

45:39.666 --> 45:41.666
[dragging footsteps]
- Nora, are you okay?

45:44.625 --> 45:47.875
- I'm sorry to break this lovey dovey, whatever you guys call it.

45:49.541 --> 45:56.416
All I need to know is who else knows about the ROSS 4.4 file?

45:56.625 --> 45:58.625
[dog barking]
Please tell me what I need to know.

46:04.000 --> 46:06.000
- Please man don't do this.

46:15.000 --> 46:19.625
[screaming]
I will kill you, I promise you I will kill you!

46:23.250 --> 46:25.250
- Kill him, He talks too much.

46:27.875 --> 46:29.875
- With pleasure.

46:33.166 --> 46:35.166
[gunshot]
[grunting]

46:46.125 --> 46:48.125
[gunshots]

47:22.250 --> 47:24.250
[phone dials]

47:24.916 --> 47:26.916
[phone rings]

47:29.541 --> 47:33.041
- Ayanda, where are you?
- I'm at Lerato's house.

47:33.750 --> 47:36.375
- Okay I want you to stay there.
- What's going on?

47:36.625 --> 47:39.250
- It's not safe for you to be home alone.
I'm coming to you now.

47:40.041 --> 47:41.666
- Okay.

47:41.791 --> 47:43.791
♪♪

47:57.625 --> 47:59.625
♪♪

48:12.250 --> 48:14.250
- Ayanda.

48:36.625 --> 48:38.625
♪♪

48:59.625 --> 49:02.500
- When I tell you to run, you run all right?
- All right.

49:06.041 --> 49:08.041
- Ayanda run.

49:08.291 --> 49:10.291
[gunshots]

49:24.750 --> 49:26.750
[gunshots continue]

50:15.291 --> 50:17.291
- Ayanda?
Ayanda!

51:25.125 --> 51:27.125
[door opens]

51:29.125 --> 51:30.500
[sniffles]

51:30.875 --> 51:39.125
- Aw no, no, no well
look what you made me do.

51:44.291 --> 51:47.166
You beautiful girl.

51:48.000 --> 51:50.666
- Don't touch me, you old retarded fool.

51:51.125 --> 51:53.125
[laughs amusedly]

51:57.500 --> 51:59.791
[fires empty gun]

52:03.875 --> 52:05.500
[sniffles]
[empty gun drops]

52:05.625 --> 52:11.875
Did you honestly think that I would leave a loaded gun in the room!

52:59.250 --> 53:01.791
- Hey Nkosi, get in the car.

53:02.000 --> 53:03.875
Get in the car.
- What do you want man.

53:04.000 --> 53:07.125
- Nkosi if this was my choice, I was going to kill you right now and get done with it.
- Where are you taking me to?

53:07.375 --> 53:11.291
- Get in the car!
Get in the car, now!

53:14.500 --> 53:16.500
[door closes]

53:23.500 --> 53:26.750
[water splashes]
[breathes heavily]

53:33.166 --> 53:35.750
- Nkosi. Nkosi, Nkosi.

53:36.250 --> 53:41.875
Who else knows about the ROSS 4.4?
I want to know man.

53:42.000 --> 53:46.041
Who did you tell about the ROSS 4.4?
[grunting]

53:49.375 --> 53:55.750
Come on Nkosi, just give me what I want to know.
Come on Nkosi. Just give me what I want to know.

53:56.000 --> 54:03.041
[grunting]
Come on Nkosi, you're making me mad.

54:05.000 --> 54:10.000
Nkosi, just give me what I want.
Give me what I want Nkosi.

54:16.875 --> 54:21.375
- Who's paying you man?
-Shut up! I'm the one who's asking questions here.

54:23.250 --> 54:28.875
[grunting]
Come on, look at me. Nkosi come on.

54:31.916 --> 54:39.250
Nkosi come on, I'm going to shoot you man.
I don't mind pulling this trigger, right here right now.

54:39.750 --> 54:45.041
I'm going to kill you Nkosi.
Just give me what I want to know. Shut up!

54:46.916 --> 54:49.791
[breathes heavily]
Eish.

54:54.916 --> 55:00.125
- Here's some food for you my man. Grab something to eat.
I'll drop it here.

55:00.541 --> 55:02.875
- How am I supposed to eat tied up?

55:03.666 --> 55:08.791
- Okay, let me try to untie it and see how you will be come loose.

55:08.916 --> 55:10.541
- Thank you man.
- Okay.

55:13.375 --> 55:15.375
[heart beating]

55:27.791 --> 55:29.791
[knuckles cracking]

55:51.875 --> 55:54.916
- Get up and take me to whoever is paying you.
- What if I don't Nkosi?

55:55.875 --> 55:57.875
[gunshot]
[grunting]

55:58.875 --> 56:02.500
- The next one is going in your head.

56:06.125 --> 56:07.666
- It's minister Bernard.

56:07.875 --> 56:09.875
- What? What minister?
- Yes.
- Minster Bernard.

56:11.291 --> 56:14.541
- Yes. [grunting intensifies]
Nkosi!

56:14.666 --> 56:20.250
- I'm taking your tekkies, you won't need them for some time.
- Shit Nkosi.

56:35.166 --> 56:37.166
[gunshots]

56:49.250 --> 56:51.250
[gunshots]

58:12.041 --> 58:14.041
[grunting]

58:20.750 --> 58:22.750
[breathe heavily]

58:34.250 --> 58:36.250
[water splashes]

59:30.000 --> 59:32.000
[gunshots]

59:46.375 --> 59:48.375
[gunfire]

59:49.166 --> 59:56.750
- So... you're not a cat after all? Nine lives.
[grunting]

1:00:01.125 --> 1:00:02.500
[gunfire]
- Aah!

1:00:03.000 --> 1:00:07.791
- HIV is not a death sentence you bloody fool.
[grunting]

1:00:21.250 --> 1:00:23.250
♪♪

1:00:40.500 --> 1:00:43.666
[car door opens, closes]

1:00:49.750 --> 1:00:52.125
- Welcome back sir, Mr Bernard is dead.

1:00:52.291 --> 1:00:54.291
- Good riddance, you know what to do.

1:00:57.041 --> 1:01:01.125
[car door opens, closes]

1:01:02.791 --> 1:01:04.791
[engine revving]
[tyres screeching]

1:01:15.916 --> 1:01:17.916
♪♪

1:01:34.291 --> 1:01:39.000
- Good day Mr. President.
- Mr. Nkosi please, take a seat.

1:01:40.500 --> 1:01:47.250
- Firstly, I want to thank you for exposing Minister Bernard.
The rats that he is.

1:01:47.875 --> 1:01:49.125
- It's a pleasure sir.

1:01:49.250 --> 1:01:57.416
- Good. I'm the one who actually authorized your release
once the papers were brought to my attention and we reviewed it.

1:01:58.291 --> 1:02:03.250
Look um, I want to apologize on behalf of the government
for throwing into jail.

1:02:04.291 --> 1:02:09.000
You're one of our top undercover detectives,
we should have protected you.

1:02:09.625 --> 1:02:15.375
Now, having said that,
I need you to tell me everything you know about ROSS 4.4.

1:02:15.875 --> 1:02:19.166
- Mr. President, permission to speak freely please?

1:02:19.375 --> 1:02:20.750
- Permission granted.

1:02:21.000 --> 1:02:23.750
- I know that's a big government cover up sir.

1:02:24.125 --> 1:02:31.375
- This isn't a government cover up.
I can't say what it is myself but then again that's why you're here.

1:02:31.625 --> 1:02:37.875
If there's anyone who can get to the bottom of this, it's you.
These people need to be stopped.

1:02:38.500 --> 1:02:43.375
You can imagine the risks to the lives out there if we don't stop them.

1:02:43.875 --> 1:02:46.625
You do understand don't you?
- Yes sir.

1:02:46.750 --> 1:02:50.666
- Good. Please, come with me. [sighs]

1:02:51.541 --> 1:02:53.541
♪♪

1:03:08.041 --> 1:03:11.000
Hello Nora, are you there? Can you hear me?

1:03:11.041 --> 1:03:14.875
[gun cocks]
- Yes I'm here. I'm just waiting for the lady who said she has information for me.

1:03:14.875 --> 1:03:17.250
- I need to tell you what the president and I spoke about.

1:03:17.291 --> 1:03:19.791
- I'll see just now.

1:03:23.541 --> 1:03:28.000
- Thanks for meeting me, we don't have much time
and I think they might be following me. [breathes heavily]

1:03:28.166 --> 1:03:31.625
- Wait, relax. Who might be following you?

1:03:31.666 --> 1:03:35.875
- The company I work for.
- What company? You said you have information for me.

1:03:36.000 --> 1:03:36.666
- Yes, yes.
- Let's talk.

1:03:36.875 --> 1:03:43.916
- I'm among a group of doctors that are recently hired by a company
and there's a section of the company we weren't supposed to go to

1:03:44.000 --> 1:03:46.416
and yesterday I went there.
- What happened?

1:03:46.750 --> 1:03:51.125
Have you heard of Project Coast?
- Chemical weapon project?

1:03:51.416 --> 1:03:52.291
[breathes heavily] - Yes.
-Ya.

1:03:52.625 --> 1:03:56.791
- The company has restarted Project Coast
and they're experimenting on black people.

1:03:57.166 --> 1:04:05.750
[car door opens] Here's everything I've managed to print of the company
and I'm sure the company is behind the killings of people living with HIV.

1:04:06.250 --> 1:04:08.000
- Wait, what's the name of the company?

1:04:08.125 --> 1:04:13.000
- I don't work for the company, I quit this morning.
Please don't look for me, I don't work for the company anymore.

1:04:13.125 --> 1:04:15.125
[gunshots]

1:04:38.375 --> 1:04:43.000
- Please call the ambulance.
Can someone call the ambulance please?

1:04:48.541 --> 1:04:53.416
[recording] "the company has restarted Project Coast
and they are experimenting on black people..."

1:04:55.875 --> 1:04:58.250
[glass thudding]

1:05:00.500 --> 1:05:03.000
[screaming indistinctly]
- I don't want to die

1:05:04.250 --> 1:05:06.625
[glass thudding]
- Get me out of here Please

1:05:08.166 --> 1:05:10.500
[glass thudding]

1:05:20.875 --> 1:05:27.625
- Do you really think you have a choice in life? No. [chuckles]

1:05:28.500 --> 1:05:31.416
[echoing] Your choices are given to you.

1:05:36.916 --> 1:05:38.916
Let's begin phase two.
